import {HorizontalGridLines, LineSeries, VerticalBarSeries, XAxis, XYPlot, YAxis} from "react-vis";

let data = [
    {x: 1, y: 10},
    {x: 2, y: 11},
    {x: 3, y: 9},
    {x: 4, y: 11},
    {x: 5, y: 10},
    {x: 6, y: 10},
    {x: 7, y: 10},
    {x: 8, y: 10},
    {x: 9, y: 10},
    {x: 10, y: 10},
    {x: 11, y: 10},
    {x: 12, y: 10},
]

export const Graph = () => {
    return (
        <XYPlot
            width={1500}
            height={300}>
            <HorizontalGridLines/>
            <LineSeries data={data} />
            <XAxis/>
            <YAxis/>
        </XYPlot>
    )
}
